===Pronunciation===
*ἐσθίω / esthiō / es-thee'-o
=== Etymology ===

*Strengthened for a primary word [[ἔδω]] edō (to eat); used only in certain tenses, the rest being supplied by [[φάγω]] {{GG|5315}}; 
=== Verb ===
to [[eat]] (usually literally): - [[devour]], eat, [[live]].